Hiya Phil nice to see you here. All of Frank&#39;s boxes are made by Frank himself. If you want to make something quick you can make yourself can try one of the hacks or manual sweep. Heres a couple links for you on how to modify some radios. Mike C. and Steve H. have been kind enough to demonstrate it for you guys in some how to videos. 

Mike&#39;s website
