Misty

--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com, &quot;pollux41101&quot; &lt;kentuckyghosthunter@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt; Just wanted to say hello to the group and that I am very happy to be a part of this community.
&gt; 
&gt; My name is Phil and I&#39;ve been doing research (in and out of the field) into the paranormal for several years.  
&gt; 
&gt; As it stands I&#39;m looking to expand my knowledge and technical base in EVP research.
&gt; 
&gt; I&#39;ve done some searching through the board and files here and I have found myself somewhat perplexed by the variety of different boxes and hacks available.
&gt; 
&gt; I would much appreciate it if someone could point me in the direction of a good box schematic to build that&#39;s relatively reliable (doesn&#39;t have to be bleeding edge or anything) and somewhat current.  
&gt; 
&gt; Is it best to grab one of the box schematics floating around or is a RS Hack the way to begin?  And which schematic/hack would be best to start with?
&gt; 
&gt; I apologize for the completely bland question, but it&#39;s difficult to decipher what&#39;s current and what is not and what&#39;s best to start with through the posts I&#39;ve found up to this point.
&gt; 
&gt; I appreciate any and all help anyone could offer and I look forward to getting to you all and working with the community.
&gt; 
&gt; Thanks,
&gt; -Phil
